{"tid":2107690,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲日本女偶像驟逝！　死因成謎「生前最後留言」藏弔詭疑團","createTime":"2020-07-14T04:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T07:02:49.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5fbdebffee3548e604bf296e5203afdc77f8e88f","tid":2107690,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T04:44:42.000Z","msg":"又有偶像傳出輕生！日本女團KissBee的成員鷹野日南13日傳出死訊，經紀公司以聲明證實不幸消息，聲明中提到為了遵照家人的意願，一直等到喪事結束後才公開消息，鷹野日南實際是在10日離世，得年20歲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5001/d5001433.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5001%2Fd5001433.jpg&h=fe7c9952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自鷹野日南IG）<br />\n<br />\nKissBee除了是少女團體，同時也經營YouTube頻道，有26萬名網友追蹤，聲勢正旺的她們更曾在2018年的網路票選中，獲選為「Next Break Idol（潛力偶像）」，因此當鷹野日南的死訊公開後，粉絲相當錯愕。<br />\n<br />\n網友湧入鷹野日南推特哀悼時發現，她最後一則發文正是停留在10日，當時留下意味深長的文字，「因為有大家，我才能走到現在，感謝！」看似像粉絲告白的話，如今外界看來更像是遺言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5001/5001434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2-ettoday-net.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5001%2F5001434.jpg&h=0f082e96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／翻攝自鷹野日南推特）<br />\n<br />\n不過至今經紀公司並未公開鷹野日南的死因，日本媒體推斷可能是輕生，而其他團員及身邊的工作人員因為一時之間無法接受鷹野日南過世的事實，為了照顧藝人及工作人員的心理狀態，團體將會暫時停止活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1759842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1759842&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnyLuFcS90NLYcDmgyrq2hhY%3D&h=c0445ca5\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1759842</a>"},{"pid":"f857e0b39b57d8e0f8ae615d85beb33ed9ff318e","tid":2107690,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"寫埋遺書仲唔係自殺?"},{"pid":"9cd804da2e908f05bc6f62e6a3e30f0643dcb7fd","tid"